<br>
When I logged back in, the wolf and the broodmother were attacking me again.  Logged off, stayed logged off longer this time.<br>
<br>
<br>
Logged back in, found wolf and broodmother.  Wolf agro'd, broodmother didn't.  I handed in the control harness, and broodmother agro'd.  I thought I was going to have to start over.   Ran off a bit, camped for 5 minutes.<br>
<br>
When I came back, there was no wolf, and the broodmother was headed toward the giant fort.  I followed invis.  She attacked one giant, the other ran off.  I followed and snared it.<br>
<br>
The broodmother came to his aid, and she resisted every snare.  But, I noticed  that if the giant stayed rooted, she stayed by his side.  Kept roots and dots on the giant.  When the giant died, the broodmother poofed.<br>
<br>
